SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 1000Z TO 1900Z DAILY
   24 AND 25 MAR WITHIN 60 MILES OF
   57-02.0N 009-07.4W. VESSELS INTENDING
   TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT HEBRIDES
   RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 491/10.
3. CANCEL THIS MSG 252000Z MAR.
